<div class="about-background">
  <img src="/assets/images/blob.svg" alt="" />
  <div class="photo-profile">
    <img src="/assets/images/photo_profile.jpg" />
  </div>
  <div class="text">
    <p class="text__top">
      Welcome to my site ! I'm a junior frontend developer based in Versailles,
